---
title: Panko Crusted Salmon and Potato Wedges with roasted cherry tomatoes and courgette
description: Perfectly pink salmon is coated with crispy breadcrumbs and paired with tender roast tomatoes and courgette in a nourishing recipe that also features a sumptuous sauce and golden crispy potato wedges.
